      "actionDesc": "Introduced in Senate",
      "text": "<p><strong>Wildland Firefighters Congressional Gold Medal Act</strong></p><p>This bill provides for the award of a Congressional Gold Medal to wildland firefighters in recognition of their strength, resiliency, sacrifice, and service to protect the forests, grasslands, and communities of the United States.</p>",
